### **4. 32_ChartFluxViewer**  
**Description:**  
Displays real-time numeric values as a smooth scrolling line chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# ChartFluxViewer - Real-Time Data Visualizer

ChartFluxViewer turns raw numeric streams into a fluid chart visualization for dashboards, sensors, or demos.

## Features
- Real-time updates  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Built with Matplotlib  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_ChartFluxViewer.git
cd 32_ChartFluxViewer
python visualize.py
